In order for you to be eligible to receive contributions from your new team members you must be at least level <1>. Level <1> contributions are only directed to Level <1> members or greater. To advance to level <1> Click the Advance to level <1> link. If you are NOT at level <1>, when one of your team members pays to advance to level <1>, you will not be included as one of the payees. Level <1> contributions are $1 or $10, depending on the advancing team members position.

Team members in position 1 advancing to level <1> $1 contribution.
Team members in position 2 advancing to level <1> $1 contribution.
Team members in position 3 advancing to level <1> $1 contribution.
Team members in position 4 advancing to level <1> $10 contribution.